About this item

  • Transparent design: Immerse your gaming space with the ZEB-Max Link Pro wireless gamepad that comes in vibrant RGB LED lights illuminating the transparent gamepad, adding a dynamic and lively ambiance to your console.
  • Compatibility: Ensure a smooth gaming experience across various platforms, as it also provides support for PS3, PS4, Windows,iOS and Android (depending upon device & game compatibility).
  • Dual Mode: Enjoy the freedom of wireless gaming with Bluetooth connectivity, or switch to wired mode for uninterrupted gameplay.
  • Macro buttons: The gamepad comes with 19 buttons for precise control including programmable macro buttons that let gamers map multiple actions to a single button, making repetitive moves effortless.
  • Extended lifespan: Experience prolonged gaming sessions with the ZEB-Max Link Pro, equipped with a built-in rechargeable battery and type-C charging, boasting an impressive lifespan of up to 10* hours (*without RGB light, depending upon usage conditions). Charge effortlessly via the dock port and enjoy high-quality audio through the 3.5mm jack for an uninterrupted gaming experience

    How are ratings calculated?
    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    Customers say

    Customers find the gamepad's build quality amazing, with sturdy sticks and good value for money. The functionality and connectivity receive mixed feedback - while it works well with laptop games, some report connectivity issues, particularly with Bluetooth. The buttons and vibration features also get mixed reviews, with some finding them responsive while others note the triggers aren't pressure sensitive and the vibration motors don't work properly. The support for games is mixed, with some saying it supports all games while others report it doesn't work with specific devices like Samsung S24.

      1.0 out of 5 stars Don't buy it!!!
      Reviewed in India on 3 October 2024
      Style Name: Zeb-Max LinkVerified Purchase
      The product is great and has a long battery life. I would say atleast 8 to 9 hrs. However the problem arises when charging or when the battery is low. It won't show you that the battery is low or doesn't emits light when it's battery is low. When the battery is totlly out it stops working that is how you know that the remote doesn't have ny more juice. Even when charging with the given USB type C it doesn't charges properly and you have to connect to a mobile charger to charge it then again the light goes out and you won't know if it is fully charge. It's one of the major draw back in this remote. If only the manufacturer gave a light to signal out the battery percentage it would have been great for which I have deducted 1 star for this product.

      Edit:: after using for one month here are few things which I am suffering from.

      1. You won't know if the battery is full.
      2. You won't know if the battery is going to run out.
      3. As mentioned in its instruction it's USB cable doens't works.
      4. Can't use when plugged in for charging.
      5. Can't reset as there is no clear instructions
      6. While playing the game all the light in the indicator will light up and it will get disconnected.
      7. You won't get any recommendations or help from the company as there is not much available in the website or in the internet.

      My RECOMMENDATION DONT BUY IT
